[SPEAKER_00] a imaš većinu njih koja nemaju to.

1343
01:16:41,000 --> 01:16:42,939
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, on te ne može tražiti osnovne ulici u Americi.

1344
01:16:42,939 --> 01:16:45,539
[SPEAKER_00] I ne moraš nizlaziti iz auta i tako stavljaju nekim državama.

1345
01:16:45,539 --> 01:16:47,579
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ono, ovisi ako je...

1346
01:16:47,579 --> 01:16:49,359
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, nije gazit, ne?

1347
01:16:49,460 --> 01:16:50,680
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ono, to je problem.

1348
01:16:50,680 --> 01:16:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ono, ne moraš izaći, ne moraš mu se pokoravati,

1349
01:16:53,500 --> 01:16:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] ne moraš mu se obraćati sa, ono, da, gazda,

1350
01:16:55,460 --> 01:16:58,600
[SPEAKER_00] evo, gospodar, može reciti što da radim,

1351
01:16:58,600 --> 01:16:59,720
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne me ga gazit.

1352
01:16:59,720 --> 01:17:01,920
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da, nisam ni mislio to, da, gospod, nego naš.

1353
01:17:01,920 --> 01:17:04,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ne me gazit čovjeka autom, na dužnosti i sve u redu.

1354
01:17:04,659 --> 01:17:07,039
[SPEAKER_00] Mogla si prosjedovati, mogla si stavati sa strane,

1355
01:17:07,039 --> 01:17:09,319
[SPEAKER_00] vikat mu da je gestapo, da je ovde, ono,

1356
01:17:09,319 --> 01:17:10,859
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne me ga gazit autom i sve u redu.

1357
01:17:10,859 --> 01:17:12,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ono to shvatio, vratno, kao pretnja.

1358
01:17:12,460 --> 01:17:14,659
[SPEAKER_00] Da, i je bila pretnja jer ga je skoro ubila, ono.

1359
01:17:14,659 --> 01:17:16,699
[SPEAKER_00] I, ono, normalno da će svakove stavaci brajiti.

1360
01:17:16,699 --> 01:17:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ista stvar mi je u Hrvatskoj.

1361
01:17:17,960 --> 01:17:19,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ako poštojemo sve zakone,

1362
01:17:19,840 --> 01:17:22,399
[SPEAKER_00] policija neka bavlja svoju dužnost, znaš.

1363
01:17:22,399 --> 01:17:23,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to se često ne događa.

1364
01:17:23,960 --> 01:17:26,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, oni zlorabe svoje, svoje pozicije

1365
01:17:26,460 --> 01:17:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] da bi protuzakonito, nezakonito postupali.

1366
01:17:29,460 --> 01:17:31,779
[SPEAKER_00] I, ono, naravno, kad se to dogodi, da poludim.

1367
01:17:31,779 --> 01:17:33,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, naravno, da, da, da, da podivljam,

1368
01:17:33,340 --> 01:17:35,760
[SPEAKER_00] kad vidim da, policajac, da je policajac umislio

1369
01:17:35,760 --> 01:17:36,560
[SPEAKER_00] da je on moj gospodar.

1370
01:17:36,739 --> 01:17:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] Nisi, frende, moj gospodar.

1371
01:17:38,420 --> 01:17:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti radiš svoj posao, ja imam svoja prava

1372
01:17:41,000 --> 01:17:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] i ti imaš svoje oblasti.

1373
01:17:42,380 --> 01:17:44,979
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš ti meni ništa zapovijedati

1374
01:17:44,979 --> 01:17:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] da ja radim, ako ne, izlazim iz zakonskih okvira.

1375
01:17:48,159 --> 01:17:49,979
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ja stojim na javnoj površini,

1376
01:17:49,979 --> 01:17:52,680
[SPEAKER_00] šta god da radim, mogu se maskirati koliko hoću.

1377
01:17:52,680 --> 01:17:54,779
[SPEAKER_00] To zvoljeno je zakonom.

1378
01:17:54,779 --> 01:17:56,600
[SPEAKER_00] A onda promijeni zakon, frende,

1379
01:17:56,600 --> 01:17:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] pa reci da su sunčene naočele i covid maske zabranjene,

1380
01:17:59,159 --> 01:18:02,100
[SPEAKER_00] i onda se neću nositi covid masku

1381
01:18:02,100 --> 01:18:03,479
[SPEAKER_00] i sunčene naočele ispred banke.

1382
01:18:03,479 --> 01:18:05,479
[SPEAKER_00] Reci da je zabranjeno, neću to raditi.

1383
01:18:05,539 --> 01:18:06,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ako to nije zabranjeno,

1384
01:18:06,640 --> 01:18:08,279
[SPEAKER_00] pa ne možeš ti meni kaj dolaziti.

1385
01:18:08,279 --> 01:18:09,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš ti meni kaj mene tražiti.

1386
01:18:09,880 --> 01:18:11,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ako to nije zabranjeno.

1387
01:18:11,699 --> 01:18:13,560
[SPEAKER_00] I još me tam pretresa kod kriminalica,

1388
01:18:13,560 --> 01:18:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] i postavlja mi se, dere mi se tam prijateljim privođenjem,

1389
01:18:15,960 --> 01:18:16,340
[SPEAKER_00] ovo ono.

1390
01:18:16,340 --> 01:18:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo ti vidiš da je to čovjek koji ima ozbiljne probleme u život.

1391
01:18:20,079 --> 01:18:22,619
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, ja se neću, ali...

1392
01:18:22,619 --> 01:18:23,100
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nemoj da.

1393
01:18:23,100 --> 01:18:26,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ono, znaš, ti pa nemoj mi tako letavati,

1394
01:18:26,460 --> 01:18:27,140
[SPEAKER_00] sad će biti u redu.

1395
01:18:27,140 --> 01:18:28,439
[SPEAKER_00] Da je on meni uletio sa spikom,

1396
01:18:28,859 --> 01:18:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] kao ono, dobar dan, o čemu se radi?

1397
01:18:31,000 --> 01:18:33,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ne ma problema, možda bih mu čak i dao osobno.

1398
01:18:33,739 --> 01:18:36,300
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš, da mi je uletio sa spikom, ono,

1399
01:18:36,300 --> 01:18:37,760
[SPEAKER_00] dobar dan,

1400
01:18:37,760 --> 01:18:39,520
[SPEAKER_00] kaj radimo,

1401
01:18:39,520 --> 01:18:41,439
[SPEAKER_00] ja bih mu rekao, prostojam ispred banke,

1402
01:18:41,439 --> 01:18:43,319
[SPEAKER_00] imam transparent, snimam se,

1403
01:18:43,319 --> 01:18:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] sve u redu, ono,

1404
01:18:44,539 --> 01:18:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] stojim na javne površine,

1405
01:18:45,460 --> 01:18:46,739
[SPEAKER_00] ništa nisam, nisam ulazio u banku,

1406
01:18:46,739 --> 01:18:48,680
[SPEAKER_00] nisam s nisam svađu, ništa nisam...

1407
01:18:48,680 --> 01:18:50,500
[SPEAKER_00] Mi rekao bih, dobro, imate nameru ulaziti u banku?

1408
01:18:50,500 --> 01:18:51,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, imate nameru s svađu s nima?

1409
01:18:51,699 --> 01:18:53,020
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, imate nameru raditi nešto drugo?

1410
01:18:53,020 --> 01:18:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, dobro, hvala, dobiđenja.

1411
01:18:55,000 --> 01:18:55,920
[SPEAKER_00] To je tako je trebalo izgled.

1412
01:18:55,920 --> 01:18:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je trebalo izgled.

1413
01:18:57,000 --> 01:18:59,600
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, dobar dan, ili imate kakve planove?

1414
01:18:59,600 --> 01:19:01,979
[SPEAKER_00] Nemam, to je to, stojim tu ispred banke, snimam se.

1415
01:19:01,979 --> 01:19:04,060
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, hvala, dobiđenja.

1416
01:19:14,539 --> 01:19:15,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ja prijavim njih nazad, ono,

1417
01:19:15,680 --> 01:19:16,800
[SPEAKER_00] rekao bih, nisu imali značke,

1418
01:19:16,800 --> 01:19:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] nisu imali iskaznice,

1419
01:19:17,539 --> 01:19:18,560
[SPEAKER_00] nisu mi pokazali značke,

1420
01:19:18,560 --> 01:19:19,479
[SPEAKER_00] nisu imali kape,

1421
01:19:19,479 --> 01:19:21,479
[SPEAKER_00] nezakonito me legitimirao,

1422
01:19:21,479 --> 01:19:22,680
[SPEAKER_00] nezakonito me pretresao,

1423
01:19:22,680 --> 01:19:24,539
[SPEAKER_00] rekao je da me pretresao zbog nekakve, kao,

1424
01:19:24,539 --> 01:19:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] da sličim na nekakvu traženu osobu.

1425
01:19:27,159 --> 01:19:28,060
[SPEAKER_00] Ja rekao, mogu vidjeti opis?

1426
01:19:28,060 --> 01:19:28,600
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš.

1427
01:19:28,600 --> 01:19:30,819
[SPEAKER_00] Kao, nema, nema tog opisa, ne postoji.

1428
01:19:30,819 --> 01:19:32,680
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ono, kao, ja mu dam osobnu

1429
01:19:32,680 --> 01:19:34,560
[SPEAKER_00] i onda on vidi da to nije tražena osoba

1430
01:19:34,560 --> 01:19:35,720
[SPEAKER_00] i nastavi me pretresat.

1431
01:19:35,800 --> 01:19:36,779
[SPEAKER_00] Pa zaki se mi nastavio pretresati,

1432
01:19:36,779 --> 01:19:38,279
[SPEAKER_00] stari mojak se vidi da ja nisam tražena osoba

1433
01:19:38,279 --> 01:19:39,140
[SPEAKER_00] koju ti tražiš, ono.

1434
01:19:39,140 --> 01:19:41,180
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi ja kao bio maskiran pa on nije znao ko je ko.

1435
01:19:41,180 --> 01:19:43,359
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sad vidiš da nisam taj koji ti tražiš.

1436
01:19:43,359 --> 01:19:44,699
[SPEAKER_00] I zaki se mi nastavio pretresati.

1437
01:19:44,699 --> 01:19:46,100
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, nezakonito sve redom,

1438
01:19:46,100 --> 01:19:47,260
[SPEAKER_00] ja njih lijepo prijavim,

1439
01:19:47,260 --> 01:19:49,239
[SPEAKER_00] ne, ne, to ne jedan ništa veze,

1440
01:19:49,239 --> 01:19:50,859
[SPEAKER_00] oni su procijenili nešto, blablabla, ono.

1441
01:19:50,859 --> 01:19:51,979
[SPEAKER_00] I onda sam poludio,

1442
01:19:51,979 --> 01:19:52,720
[SPEAKER_00] onda sam išao sprem murje,

1443
01:19:52,720 --> 01:19:54,420
[SPEAKER_00] snimao sam aute koji ste neprupisno parkirani,

1444
01:19:54,500 --> 01:19:55,979
[SPEAKER_00] murječki, pa sam ono snima

1445
01:19:55,979 --> 01:19:57,279
[SPEAKER_00] sve koji nemaju ove značke,

1446
01:19:57,279 --> 01:19:58,319
[SPEAKER_00] iskaznice, kape i to.

1447
01:19:58,319 --> 01:19:59,560
[SPEAKER_00] I sad sam to prijavljivo

1448
01:19:59,560 --> 01:20:01,479
[SPEAKER_00] u njihovoj unutarnoj kontroli.

1449
01:20:01,479 --> 01:20:03,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa, dobijam odgovore nazad u stilu

1450
01:20:03,479 --> 01:20:05,399
[SPEAKER_00] auti nisu ometali promet,

1451
01:20:05,399 --> 01:20:06,680
[SPEAKER_00] nisu smetali prišacima,

1452
01:20:06,680 --> 01:20:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] značke su teške za uniforme,

1453
01:20:09,000 --> 01:20:10,359
[SPEAKER_00] pa ih nose u džepu, pa ono.

1454
01:20:10,359 --> 01:20:12,399
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, čekaj, pa vi ne poštojete zakon,

1455
01:20:12,399 --> 01:20:12,739
[SPEAKER_00] stani moji.

1456
01:20:12,739 --> 01:20:13,779
[SPEAKER_00] To je sve u zakonu.

1457
01:20:13,779 --> 01:20:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] Morate se identificirati

1458
01:20:14,920 --> 01:20:16,100
[SPEAKER_00] kada se čovjek traži

1459
01:20:16,100 --> 01:20:18,279
[SPEAKER_00] policijsku iskaznicu i značku na uvid.

1460
01:20:18,380 --> 01:20:19,739
[SPEAKER_00] Morate, piša u zakonu,

1461
01:20:19,739 --> 01:20:22,060
[SPEAKER_00] morate, oni neće.

1462
01:20:22,060 --> 01:20:23,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ba, bio sam nedan na trgu

1463
01:20:23,819 --> 01:20:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] na dočekoru kometaša

1464
01:20:24,960 --> 01:20:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] i ponio sam hosovu zastavu

1465
01:20:26,880 --> 01:20:27,979
[SPEAKER_00] veliku na štapu

1466
01:20:27,979 --> 01:20:30,239
[SPEAKER_00] i prvo, pošto smo parkirali

1467
01:20:30,239 --> 01:20:31,420
[SPEAKER_00] dam na Lisinskom,

1468
01:20:31,420 --> 01:20:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] sam morao proći kroz ovaj podhodnik

1469
01:20:33,000 --> 01:20:33,880
[SPEAKER_00] i tam već mi neka

1470
01:20:33,880 --> 01:20:35,279
[SPEAKER_00] ovo ćete ju smotat,

1471
01:20:35,279 --> 01:20:36,779
[SPEAKER_00] kao ne, kao ide na neku

1472
01:20:36,779 --> 01:20:38,300
[SPEAKER_00] ono psiholočku uspiku,

1473
01:20:38,300 --> 01:20:39,779
[SPEAKER_00] kao, ovo ćete meni uslogu napraviti

1474
01:20:39,779 --> 01:20:40,319
[SPEAKER_00] pa ju smotat.

1475
01:20:40,319 --> 01:20:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao, neću, ne pali mi na pamet.

1476
01:20:41,579 --> 01:20:43,079
[SPEAKER_00] I sad prođemo tu prvu

1477
01:20:43,079 --> 01:20:44,579
[SPEAKER_00] policijsku blokadu.

1478
01:20:44,579 --> 01:20:46,319
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao, kako, motar ne zastave,

1479
01:20:46,319 --> 01:20:48,020
[SPEAKER_00] ćemo se raditi, kaj tebi.

1480
01:20:48,020 --> 01:20:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] I kao i ništa,

1481
01:20:49,380 --> 01:20:50,479
[SPEAKER_00] prođemo kroz podhodnik

1482
01:20:50,479 --> 01:20:51,039
[SPEAKER_00] i zađemo van

1483
01:20:51,039 --> 01:20:52,560
[SPEAKER_00] i sad dok trga sam je nosio normalno

1484
01:20:52,560 --> 01:20:54,119
[SPEAKER_00] i na trgu mi dođu

1485
01:20:54,119 --> 01:20:55,180
[SPEAKER_00] moljati u civilu

1486
01:20:55,180 --> 01:20:56,479
[SPEAKER_00] i kao, ajmo,

1487
01:20:56,479 --> 01:20:57,800
[SPEAKER_00] osobnavamo, ono.

1488
01:20:57,800 --> 01:20:59,140
[SPEAKER_00] I ja počnem snimat,

1489
01:20:59,140 --> 01:21:00,199
[SPEAKER_00] kao, ne možete snimat.

1490
01:21:00,199 --> 01:21:00,939
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao, kaj,

1491
01:21:00,939 --> 01:21:02,920
[SPEAKER_00] čekaj na trgu, niste.

1492
01:21:02,920 --> 01:21:04,340
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao, kaj je vama,

1493
01:21:04,340 --> 01:21:05,619
[SPEAKER_00] ono, na trgu, javna površina,

1494
01:21:05,619 --> 01:21:07,060
[SPEAKER_00] ko ne mene snimat,

1495
01:21:07,060 --> 01:21:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] pored mene HRT-ova,

1496
01:21:08,039 --> 01:21:09,939
[SPEAKER_00] ekipa, prenos rade.

1497
01:21:10,380 --> 01:21:11,239
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao, ko ne mene snimat,

1498
01:21:11,239 --> 01:21:11,739
[SPEAKER_00] kaj je tebi.

1499
01:21:11,739 --> 01:21:12,560
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš, i ono,

1500
01:21:12,560 --> 01:21:13,760
[SPEAKER_00] i sad dok sam ja to upalio,

1501
01:21:13,760 --> 01:21:14,619
[SPEAKER_00] dok sam počeo snimat,

1502
01:21:14,619 --> 01:21:16,180
[SPEAKER_00] ovoga, oni nešto,

1503
01:21:16,180 --> 01:21:17,800
[SPEAKER_00] neće se identificirati,

1504
