[SPEAKER_00] kao, neće mi pokazati ništa.

1505
01:21:18,939 --> 01:21:21,060
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao, kak da ja znam da ste i policija,

1506
01:21:21,060 --> 01:21:21,520
[SPEAKER_00] ono, kao.

1507
01:21:21,520 --> 01:21:22,840
[SPEAKER_00] I onda mi je ovak,

1508
01:21:22,840 --> 01:21:23,520
[SPEAKER_00] izvadio, značko,

1509
01:21:23,520 --> 01:21:24,100
[SPEAKER_00] doslovno napravio.

1510
01:21:24,100 --> 01:21:25,039
[SPEAKER_00] O.

1511
01:21:25,039 --> 01:21:26,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ja reku, daj,

1512
01:21:26,279 --> 01:21:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] daj, samo malo,

1513
01:21:26,960 --> 01:21:27,659
[SPEAKER_00] da vidim broj,

1514
01:21:27,659 --> 01:21:28,199
[SPEAKER_00] da vidim ovo,

1515
