[SPEAKER_00] znaš,

1516
01:21:28,439 --> 01:21:29,500
[SPEAKER_00] da stavim koga da prijavim.

1517
01:21:29,500 --> 01:21:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš,

1518
01:21:30,199 --> 01:21:32,279
[SPEAKER_00] i ovi ostali općeni su ne to napravili.

1519
01:21:32,279 --> 01:21:33,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kao, on vam je pokazao.

1520
01:21:33,380 --> 01:21:34,619
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao, stvari moja,

1521
01:21:34,619 --> 01:21:35,699
[SPEAKER_00] nije mogo mahnuti sa,

1522
01:21:35,699 --> 01:21:36,720
[SPEAKER_00] ono, ne znam,

1523
