[SPEAKER_00] s novčanikom je mogo mahnuti,

1525
01:21:38,880 --> 01:21:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] isto tako.

1526
01:21:39,380 --> 01:21:39,619
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš,

1527
01:21:39,619 --> 01:21:40,739
[SPEAKER_00] nevam pojma kaj je pokazao.

1528
01:21:40,739 --> 01:21:41,939
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nisam vidio ni da je to,

1529
01:21:41,939 --> 01:21:43,060
[SPEAKER_00] R.H. policija,

1530
01:21:43,060 --> 01:21:43,380
[SPEAKER_00] nije ime,

1531
01:21:43,380 --> 01:21:43,800
[SPEAKER_00] ni prezme,

1532
01:21:43,800 --> 01:21:44,199
[SPEAKER_00] niko je,

1533
01:21:44,199 --> 01:21:45,020
